data.description: CURRENTLY UNDER CONTRACT, SELLER WILL CONSIDER BACKUP OFFERS. SELLER OFFERING UP TO $5K IN CLOSING COST ASSISTANCE! Seeking an ideal beginning in Panama City? Come see this perfectly positioned 4-bedroom, 2-bath home that is tailored for versatile living. With its 8' ceilings, durable vinyl flooring in communal spaces, cozy bedroom carpets, and an expansive layout, this home exudes warmth and openness. Its split design ensures a unique blend of privacy and adaptability, effortlessly meeting life's evolving demands. The kitchen, fitted with a central island, becomes a culinary hub for delicious feasts. The master bedroom showcases an ample en-suite, complemented by a generous walk-in closet and a garden tub. The remaining three bedrooms are sizable, perfect as guest rooms, a home workspace, or a flex space.  Begin your mornings with tranquil water views of the expansive shimmering pond, ideal for those precious moments of calm before a busy day. For those long summer days, the nearby community pool is a short walk away. Schools, dining and local activities are all close-by. Tyndall Air Force Base is a swift 5-minute drive away.
